    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >瓦佐 是什么？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 瓦佐 中，你将扮演一只小鸟，探索程序生成的世界，那里充满了古代遗迹、魔法宝物和被遗忘的秘密。你可以独自游玩，也可以与好友一起。探索、收集资源、建造鸟巢和鸟舍，生存下来，揭开这座云雾缭绕岛屿的故事！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/69715594728861bc9331fcc792a89ee9.poster.avif?t=1771618944\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/69715594728861bc9331fcc792a89ee9.webm?t=1771618944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由飞翔</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 瓦佐 中，你扮演一只拥有近乎无限飞行能力的小鸟，但这并不意味着你可以肆意飞翔！拍打翅膀会消耗体力，消耗体力会让你的小鸟感到饥饿，而饥饿感会让你无法长时间飞行。所以，滑翔来喘口气，或者使用魔法！好好飞翔，这样你就能随心所欲地飞！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/b3384976b5c6fcf60f80eeb31c5a807e.poster.avif?t=1771618944\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/b3384976b5c6fcf60f80eeb31c5a807e.webm?t=1771618944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索奇异世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一座被奇异旋转废墟环绕的被遗忘岛屿。寻找失落魔法的痕迹，开启通往其他奇幻世界的大门。从天空中寻找线索，探索岛屿的历史。但要小心，在这个看似和平的世界里，并非一切都安全！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/6a3ebf9725cf2f04c16d120355dbfbc5.poster.avif?t=1771618944\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/6a3ebf9725cf2f04c16d120355dbfbc5.webm?t=1771618944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造自己的房子</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你在岛上找到的资源，在树上建造一座鸟舍，在探险之后，拥有一个舒适的休憩之所，或者作为你远在天涯海角的据点。用舒适的鸟巢、鲜花、枕头等等，定制你房子的内外装饰！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/b9ff36dca9fc9ef387010c2c85b64982.poster.avif?t=1771618944\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/b9ff36dca9fc9ef387010c2c85b64982.webm?t=1771618944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作物品，助您旅途顺利</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源也可用于制作各种物品！食物、工具、装备，以及能够解开世界各地隐藏秘密的魔法物品。在瓦佐岛的旅途中，充分利用您能找到的一切！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/14188b70ed0284b45697f44508dab0f5.poster.avif?t=1771618944\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/14188b70ed0284b45697f44508dab0f5.webm?t=1771618944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与好友一起畅玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不想独自游戏？别担心，你的好友可以通过在线合作模式加入你的冒险之旅！随心所欲地游玩，按照自己的节奏探索，与你的小鸟伙伴们在共享的家园中共度美好时光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/5d68e51cffd36ad5e0c84d709ba41e65.poster.avif?t=1771618944\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182050/extras/5d68e51cffd36ad5e0c84d709ba41e65.webm?t=1771618944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >飞翔：你是一只鸟，扇动翅膀，翱翔天际！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >俯冲：高速俯冲，利用动量远距离飞行！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索：飞越程序生成的广阔世界，欣赏宁静的景色！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜寻：从空中寻找地面上的线索，揭开岛屿的秘密！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作：收集资源，制作物品和装备，助你旅途顺利！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造：在树上搭建一个家，在漫长的一天后休息！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >农场：种植植物、捕鱼、烹饪，填饱肚子，强健翅膀！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义你的小鸟！改变羽毛的颜色和形状，或者制作帽子戴上！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人游戏：单人探索，或与好友在线合作！</p></li></ul>",
